{"tid":1968621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈新玩法 (非膠)","createTime":"2020-04-11T19:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T20:01:07.000Z","uid":203663,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75c05b1dbb658dd11f55c30bff53ef0a348aa945","tid":1968621,"uid":203663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"今日諗到黃色經濟圈另一種玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現時嘅黃色經濟圈係搵黃店幫襯。倒不如逆其道而行，重新定義黃色經濟圈，唔係藍店嘅店鋪就係喺黃色經濟圈內。換言之，我哋只要避開幫襯藍店，其他幫襯咩都得。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 避免鬥黃困局<br />\n因爲只要唔係藍店都幫襯得，就唔會落入鬥黃困局。<br />\n<br />\n2. 更有效擴闊黃色經濟圈<br />\n只要唔係藍嘅，就納入咗可幫襯嘅黃色經濟圈內，換言之Defult咗店鋪係黃色先，唔係黃色先剔除，個數目自然會龐大。<br />\n<br />\n各位Ching點睇？"},{"pid":"8698833b46babe0ccc6d5aca5928cbc732355dfc","tid":1968621,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:37:59.000Z","msg":"藍店一律不幫襯<br />\n其他自己選擇"},{"pid":"336964584273b4309ff1b8942c493e8121189e21","tid":1968621,"uid":203663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8698833b46babe0ccc6d5aca5928cbc732355dfc","tid":1968621,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:37:59.000Z","msg":"藍店一律不幫襯<br />\n其他自己選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:40:04.000Z","msg":"Ching講得啱。<br />\n個重點變咗避藍店，而唔係搵黃店。"},{"pid":"f750218f97a4bcbec1e2e0cfe27e10b04b262704","tid":1968621,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:41:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49084ea57d05d9e37a1328695fc202269dae7e6b","tid":1968621,"uid":23160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f750218f97a4bcbec1e2e0cfe27e10b04b262704","tid":1968621,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:41:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:42:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl